name: RESTar
tagline: RESTar, or sRESTar, is a simple RESTful API framework for java.
body:
### Welcome to RESTar Pages.
RESTar is simple java framework for RESTful API with JSON support.

This framework is developed for my small system administrator's web tools.

### Authors and Contributors
Originally created by Yonghwan SO (@sio4)

### Support or Contact
This is GPLed software and developed with my spare time. I cannot support as professional but you can make issues on github site.

Thanks.
